  "text": "Using shallow dependencies in deep HPSG parsing has been previously explored by [CITATION_1] , who used dependency constraints in schema application stage to guide HPSG tree construction (F-score was improved from 87.2% to 87.9% with a single shift-reduce dependency parser). Since the baseline parser is different, we didn't make a direct comparison here. However, it would be interesting to compare these two different ways of incorporating the dependency parser into HPSG parsing. We left it as further work.",
